g":"好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS4有1-3高清版，係咪要玩哂？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"1就好快爆,係最後打龍王有gimmick,得閒咪打<br />\n<br />\n2就開始有隊伍(固定職),難度調低哂(FC版係史上最惡DQ),打呢隻先<br />\n<br />\n3係神作(當年首賣搞到學生逃學大人射波買game,買game要食廢game骨,仲好似air max95咁四圍有搶劫案),remake版再加多左嘢,一定要玩"},{"pid":"abaf12e8e4ec6f90353089f4b77ced2206b0f99d","tid":2418481,"uid":130705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"最近見到app store有得玩<br />\n就由DQ1開始玩翻<br />\nDQ3覺得麻麻地 唔太鍾意佢個同伴系統<br />\n但劇情係幾吸引"},{"pid":"9067d31b9d685dcbf5c40570d34fe47be6c40c53","tid":2418481,"uid":106465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"接受唔到DQ11 主角個樣(髮型), 所以無入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 FF fans"},{"pid":"5da415b8f7d7b37db25d44f1fff942c69476bdaa","tid":2418481,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9067d31b9d685dcbf5c40570d34fe47be6c40c53","tid":2418481,"uid":106465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"接受唔到DQ11 主角個樣(髮型), 所以無入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 FF fans"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"我全程用dlc 套衫 帶頭巾"},{"pid":"18041274aca77bfea491d6f163fc5572d6669f88","tid":2418481,"uid":129235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8757c60e26142590aee4eba47a73307339f8c1a","tid":2418481,"uid":391184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13493226c8c787bf24cc6cd2ab96b97c751ceb23","tid":2418481,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bee8bda16f96049e313e9bbe3a674701d9baa33","tid":2418481,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"唔係無左真結局<br />\n係無得同大波妹竹達彩奈結婚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"我玩11s就係因為s多左同其他人同居既劇情